'''刘易斯瀑布'''（{{lang-en|Lewis Falls}}）是美国[[怀俄明州|怀俄明州]][[黃石國家公園|黃石國家公園]]刘易斯河的瀑布之一。<ref>{{cite web | last = | first = | authorlink = | coauthors = | date = | url = http://www.topoquest.com/map.asp?lat=44.26743&lon=-110.63572&size=l&u=5&datum=nad27&layer=DRG | title =Lewis Falls, USGS Lewis Falls (WY) Topo Map | format = Map| work = | publisher =TopoQuest USGS Quads | accessdate = 2008-06-29}}（英文）</ref>

瀑布往下冲的高度约30英尺（9.1米），可以轻易从路中观赏得到，其位置大约靠近南大门往格兰特村与公园的中途。<ref>{{cite web | last = | first = | authorlink = | coauthors = | date = | url =http://www.waterfallswest.com/wy-lewis-falls.html | title =刘易斯瀑布 | format = | work =怀俄明州刘易斯瀑布 | publisher =Waterfallswest | accessdate =2007-04-14 | archive-date =2016-03-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234050/http://www.waterfallswest.com/wy-lewis-falls.html | dead-url =no }}（英文）</ref>

